<section id="watermarks">
  <title>Watermarks</title>

  <para id="watermarksWidget"><informalexample>
      <para>To add a watermark to a printed form, double-click on the copy you
      want to add the watermark to. The following screen will appear:</para>

      <para><screenshot>
          <mediaobject>
            <imageobject>
              <imagedata fileref="images/addWatermark.png"/>
            </imageobject>

            <caption>Add Watermark</caption>
          </mediaobject>
        </screenshot></para>

      <para>When adding a watermark to a copy of a printed form, you are
      presented with the following options:</para>

      <variablelist>
        <varlistentry>
          <term>Watermark</term>

          <listitem>
            <para>Specify the name of the watermark to be used on the selected
            copy. Different copies can have different watermarks.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>

        <varlistentry>
          <term>Show Prices</term>

          <listitem>
            <para>Select to show prices on the selected copy.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
      </variablelist>
    </informalexample></para>
</section>
